          "isCorrect": true,
          "text": "Domain"
        },
        {
          "feedback": "The scheme `https` explains the lock icon, but it does not prove the page is the company’s site. The mismatch is in the domain, which names the host being visited.",
          "isCorrect": false,
          "text": "Scheme"
