          "isCorrect": true,
          "text": "Rope carried the pulse"
        },
        {
          "feedback": "The tape did not move down the line; it only moved up and down where it was attached. The rope carried the pulse because the disturbance traveled through the rope while its parts oscillated locally.",
          "isCorrect": false,
          "text": "Tape traveled with pulse"
        },
        {
          "feedback": "Air may be around the setup, but the visible bump is moving along the line itself. The rope carried the pulse because its sections moved locally as the disturbance passed.",
          "isCorrect": false,
          "text": "Air carried the pulse"
